Class DynamicDataOnMemoryFromFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.amidst.dynamic.datastream.filereaders.DynamicDataOnMemoryFromFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataOnMemory<DynamicDataInstance>, DataStream<DynamicDataInstance>, Iterable<DynamicDataInstance>

    public class DynamicDataOnMemoryFromFile
extends Object
implements DataOnMemory<DynamicDataInstance>
    The DynamicDataStreamFromFile class implements the DataOnMemory interface and loads a dynamic data on memory from a given file.
